This account is used to manage the [http://sites.imagej.net/Bio-Formats/ Bio-Formats 4 update site]. See also [[List of update sites]].

To activate it in your Fiji setup:

* [[Update_Sites|''Help>Update Fiji'']]
* Click ''Manage update sites''
* Check ''Bio-Formats daily builds''
* Click ''Close''

Five files should appear on the list with ''Status/Action'' of ''Update it''.

* Click ''Apply changes''
* Restart Fiji
* ''Help>About Plugins>LOCI Plugins...''

The dialog should now show a very recent build date (within the last few days).
